description: This taco truck is rolling its way through Raleigh, reacquainting rumbling tummies with their traditional and totally terrific tacos and tortas. With a menu that includes staples like Al Pastor, Carnitas, Barbacoa, Asada, Chorizo and more, you just pick the perfect meat for your taco treat and you walk away with a deliciously neat meal for pretty cheap - AKA the ideal Food Truck experience.After trying this fantastic fare, you’ll want to eat El Rey every day.
name: El Rey Del Taco
